- ğŸ›¡ï¸ **Sensitive Data Scanning**  
  Detects patterns such as emails, passwords, phone numbers, and API keys â€” keeping your data safer

- ğŸ§  **Text Intelligence**  
  Handy utilities to detect questions, palindromes, emojis, and even visual symbols in your text

- ğŸ§° **Expanded Utilities**  
